Description:P0 attacks with Ironclaw Orcs (2/2 red). P1 controls Circle of Protection: Red and a Plains. During P0's combat P1 activates CoP:Red choosing the red attacker, so the next time it would deal damage to P1 it is prevented (CR 615.1, 615.6). P1's life stays at 20.

